#

Carrot and Raisin Salad

15 min
$6
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Eggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

SaladEasyQuickHealthy

Description

A refreshing and crunchy salad that's sweet and tangy, perfect for any meal!

Ingredients

  • grated carrots: 2 cups
  • raisins: 1/2 cup
  • mayonnaise: 1/4 cup
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • pepper: to taste
